docstring: Sets the start line number of the code block model instance.
code_content:
def set_start_line_num(
    self, line_num: int
) -> Union[
    "BaseModelBuilder",
    "ModuleModelBuilder",
    "ClassModelBuilder",
    "FunctionModelBuilder",
]:
    """Sets the start line number of the code block model instance."""
    self.common_attributes.start_line_num = line_num
    return self
